@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cfnpws(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v0
    tmp = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.11) / (v0 + 0.06 / v1 + 0.25)) + wp.exp((v2 + 0.89 * tmp + 0.58)))
    tmp = (wp.abs(0.22) + tmp)
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.sin((v1 + 0.03 - v1 + 0.50)))
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
